## 🏗️ 서비스 클래스 구조

### TransactionCacheService ([lib/services/transaction-cache.ts](mdc:lib/services/transaction-cache.ts))

```typescript
export interface CacheLookupResult {
  found: boolean;
  uniqueKey?: string;
  source: 'cache' | 'computed';
}

export interface CacheStoreResult {
  success: boolean;
  hash: string;
  alreadyExists: boolean;
}

export interface CacheStats {
  totalLookups: number;
  cacheHits: number;
  cacheMisses: number;
  hitRate: number; // 0-1
  averageResponseTime: number; // ms
}

export class TransactionCacheService {
  async lookup(rawText: string): Promise<CacheLookupResult>;
  async store(rawText: string, uniqueKey: string): Promise<CacheStoreResult>;
  async getStats(): Promise<CacheStats>;
  async resetStats(): Promise<void>;
}
```

**성능 목표:**
- `lookup()`: < 10ms
- `store()`: < 20ms  
- `getStats()`: < 5ms

## 🌐 API 엔드포인트

### 1. 캐시 조회 API
**엔드포인트:** `POST /api/cache/lookup`
**파일:** [app/api/cache/lookup/route.ts](mdc:app/api/cache/lookup/route.ts)

```typescript
// Request
{
  rawText: string;
  companyId: string;
}

// Response  
{
  found: boolean;
  uniqueKey?: string;
  hash: string;
  responseTime: number;
}
```

### 2. 캐시 저장 API  
**엔드포인트:** `POST /api/cache/store`
**파일:** [app/api/cache/store/route.ts](mdc:app/api/cache/store/route.ts)

```typescript
// Request
{
  rawText: string;
  uniqueKey: string;
  companyId: string;
}

// Response
{
  success: boolean;
  hash: string;
  alreadyExists: boolean;
}
```

### 3. 캐시 통계 API
**엔드포인트:** `GET /api/cache/stats`  
**파일:** [app/api/cache/stats/route.ts](mdc:app/api/cache/stats/route.ts)

```typescript
// Response
{
  totalLookups: number;
  cacheHits: number;
  cacheMisses: number; 
  hitRate: number;
  averageResponseTime: number;
  period: string; // "24h", "7d", etc.
}
```

